{
  "stem": "3012.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, Mother and my uncle and my cousin's husband, who were hiding in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then eventually, the communists took everything we had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But luckily, my grandfather had a-- a summer house-- a villa-- villa, what they call it in-- in-- in Europe-- on the outskirts of town, which Mother and Auntie sold because, of course, unfortunately, they-- they became the heirs of whatever was left.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we bought a co-op in Budapest for the money they got from the house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we moved to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By that time, we, again, didn't have anything because the communists took it-- took it away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was in the-- they took away gradually.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In '48 part of it, and '49, then total nationalization.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No private enterprise.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Perhaps a doctor or two was able to function, but they did not like that, either.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, the authorities didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we moved up to Budapest, and started to work and-- all of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked first as a secretary in an architect's bureau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did correspondence.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I made translation-- I did some translation as well, and started studying music.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I always wanted to go to the opera, to work at the opera.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as it turned out-- of course, I-- I-- I never would have had a chance because of the capitalistic background, not a member of the party, our class was declared enemy of the party.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, the-- the usual communist nonsense-- this terrible, asinine ideology they have.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But luckily-- you remember the people I stayed with while I was going to school at [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Margaret Fisher, the daughter of the lady where I was staying at, had a sister, Annie Fisher.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She became a world-renown pianist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She used to come to America.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
